title: Sega Genesis(PGEN) for PS2/2 CDr
description: Sega Genesis for Ps2 ( http://pgen.gamebase.ca/downloads.php ) . I made this Image with Nero, but you can use any program to burn it, as long as it burns image files.    You can play it on PS2 assuming you have a ps2 that has a MOD-CHIP or you are using a SWAP DISC and some kind of boot method. It includes 2 Cdr images which both have 474 games on each cd a total of 948 games.
